Definition 1.3.8. Let $\mathcal{C}$ be a Krull-Schmidt category and $\mathbf{P}$ a pairwise compatibility condition such that $\mathbf{P}$ induces the $\mathbf{P}$-cluster theory of $\mathcal{C}$. If for every $\mathbf{P}$-cluster $T$ and $X\in T$ there is a $\mathbf{P}$-mutation at $X$ then we call $\mathscr{T}_{\mathbf{P}}(\mathcal{C})$ the tilting $\mathbf{P}$-cluster theory.
Definition 3.3.10. Let $m\geq 1$ be an integer. If $m$ is even define $(G_{m}^{m+1},\xi_{m}^{m+1}):=(F_{m}^{m+1},\eta_{m}^{m+1})$ (Definition 3.2.1). If $m$ is odd we define $(G_{m}^{m+1},\xi_{m}^{m+1})$ in a similar, but distinct, way. Let $T_{\mathbf{N}_{m}}$ be an $\mathbf{N}_{m}$ cluster for odd $m$. Define $\displaystyle G_{m}^{m+1}(T_{\mathbf{N}_{m}})$ $\displaystyle=\{(i+1)\leavevmode\hbox to14.64pt{\vbox to6.11pt{\pgfpicture% \makeatletter\hbox to 0.0pt{\pgfsys@beginscope\pgfsys@invoke{ }\definecolor{% pgfstrokecolor}{rgb}{0,0,0}\pgfsys@color@rgb@stroke{0}{0}{0}\pgfsys@invoke{ }% \pgfsys@color@rgb@fill{0}{0}{0}\pgfsys@invoke{ }\pgfsys@setlinewidth{0.4pt}% \pgfsys@invoke{ }\nullfont\pgfsys@beginscope\pgfsys@invoke{ }\pgfsys@invoke{% \lxSVG@closescope }\pgfsys@endscope\hbox to 0.0pt{\pgfsys@beginscope% \pgfsys@invoke{ }{}{{}}{} {}{}{}\pgfsys@moveto{0.0pt}{0.0pt}\pgfsys@lineto{8.535827pt}{0.0pt}% \pgfsys@stroke\pgfsys@invoke{ } {}{{}}{}{{{}} {}{}{}{}{}{}{}{} }{}\pgfsys@moveto{0.0pt}{0.0pt}\pgfsys@moveto{0.853583pt}{0.0pt}% \pgfsys@curveto{0.853583pt}{0.471421pt}{0.471421pt}{0.853583pt}{0.0pt}{0.85358% 3pt}\pgfsys@curveto{-0.471421pt}{0.853583pt}{-0.853583pt}{0.471421pt}{-0.85358% 3pt}{0.0pt}\pgfsys@curveto{-0.853583pt}{-0.471421pt}{-0.471421pt}{-0.853583pt}% {0.0pt}{-0.853583pt}\pgfsys@curveto{0.471421pt}{-0.853583pt}{0.853583pt}{-0.47% 1421pt}{0.853583pt}{0.0pt}\pgfsys@closepath\pgfsys@moveto{0.0pt}{0.0pt}% \pgfsys@fillstroke\pgfsys@invoke{ } {}{{}}{}{{{}} {}{}{}{}{}{}{}{} }{}\pgfsys@moveto{8.535827pt}{0.0pt}\pgfsys@moveto{9.38941pt}{0.0pt}% \pgfsys@curveto{9.38941pt}{0.471421pt}{9.007248pt}{0.853583pt}{8.535827pt}{0.8% 53583pt}\pgfsys@curveto{8.064406pt}{0.853583pt}{7.682244pt}{0.471421pt}{7.6822% 44pt}{0.0pt}\pgfsys@curveto{7.682244pt}{-0.471421pt}{8.064406pt}{-0.853583pt}{% 8.535827pt}{-0.853583pt}\pgfsys@curveto{9.007248pt}{-0.853583pt}{9.38941pt}{-0% .471421pt}{9.38941pt}{0.0pt}\pgfsys@closepath\pgfsys@moveto{8.535827pt}{0.0pt}% \pgfsys@fillstroke\pgfsys@